An investment firm, Anchoria Asset Management, has unveiled plans to deploy technology to design innovative financial products and solutions in the industry to remain attractive to customers. The Managing Director of the company, Azubike Emodi while speaking at the firm’s Client Summit & Brand Re-launch held in Lagos at the weekend, said the company was poised to continue to improve on its process, explore broader investment possibilities and churn out innovative solutions to enhance its competitiveness in the industry and stay ahead of trends. According to him, these solutions would provide all investment needs of its customers, especially in the areas of saving towards retirement, for education, purchase of an asset, or any other lifestyle plans. “With the brand re-launch, what we promise our dear clients is simple; Excellence. In line with this promise we also introduce our financial technology platform – SEEDs by AnchoriaAM. “This platform presents not only access to key financial market information, but also access to subscribe to our products, create unique portfolios and manage your investments in (local & foreign currencies) on the go.” Emodi said the company had transitioned into becoming one of the top market leaders in the industry within six years of operations. He added that the firm targets to be among the top three market leaders in terms of asset management, clientele services and relevance in the market with the debut of its new financial technology product in the next five years. “We have deployed innovative products that have helped expand our reach and provided varying safe and rewarding investment options for our clients. “With these, we have seen steady growth in our assets under management, the scale of operations and profitability. Today, we witness a re-launch of the Anchoria Asset Management brand, we aim to be the leading investment solutions provider, delivering best-in-class”, he said. 